msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guimenu>System modifications</guimenu> lists all modifications performed on the default SELinux policy. If you want to export the modifications and reuse them on different servers, click <guimenu>View automation script</guimenu> . In the new window, you can copy a shell script or the ansible configuration file that can be applied on other servers."
msgstr ""

