msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing updates"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guimenu>Check for Updates</guimenu> to get a list of new package updates and patches available for your system. You can view each package update or patch information by clicking the blue icon next to the package update/patch. It is recommended to install the patches marked as important as soon as possible."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2291
#, no-c-format
msgid "To apply the updates and patches, click <guimenu>Update and Reboot</guimenu> . The equivalent of the <command>transactional-update up</command> command is called, and a new snapshot of your system is created. After the update completes successfully, your system will be rebooted and the new snapshot set as default."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2298
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can postpone the reboot of your system after the update process by selecting <guimenu>Update without Reboot</guimenu> from the three dots menu. Bear in mind that you need to reboot the system to activate the snapshot with updates. If you perform further changes without rebooting the system beforehand, a new snapshot will be created from the same point as the snapshots with updates. Therefore, the new snapshot will not include the updates."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2307
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also update &slema; using CLI. For details, refer to <xref linkend=\"sec-command-list\"/> ."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Performing rollbacks"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2314
#, no-c-format
msgid "In <literal>Snapshots &amp; Updates</literal> you can perform a rollback to one of older snapshots by clicking <guimenu>Rollback and Reboot</guimenu> , or <guimenu>Rollback without Reboot</guimenu> in the three dots menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid "After rebooting the system, the snapshot you rolled back to will be set as active. Do not make any changes (install updates, packages, etc.) before rebooting your system, as the snapshot you rolled back to is not active. Any changes performed before you reboot your system will start from the currently active snapshot."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: art_admin_slemicro_cockpit.xml:2326
#, no-c-format
msgid "For a system rollback procedure performed using CLI, refer to <xref linkend=\"sec-rollback-procedure\"/> ."
msgstr ""

